title: Quantum Physics Meets Kabbalah
description:
This torrent contains 5 videos of the partially recorded symposium in two days meeting between a kabbalist scientist Rav Michael Laitman, PhD
( http://www.arionline.info/mlaitman.php ) & and quantum scientists + an HTML page with additional information.

By Bnei Baruch Center for Kabbalah studies (http://kabbalah.info, http://www.arionline.info, http://www.kab.tv/eng).
